metadata.name: The Maiden
metadata.description:
The Maiden is a hacker, anarchist and primary antagonist from the Tales of Nexus lore. Little is known about her, but she is said to have infamous reputation within the dark circles of her world and is feared by all who know her name. 

This piece by artist, Ignis captures The Maiden during her "mindscape" - a state in which see can see visions of both past, present and future alike. 

This mint will be split with the artist as well as the Tales of Nexus creative team.
